# CodeAct × Monty agent example
#
# This example runs fully offline with a deterministic model (`DemoLlm`) and a
# sandboxed Python interpreter — no API keys or environment variables are
# required to run it.
#
# `cargo run` works out of the box. The variable below is optional and only
# affects log verbosity.

# Optional: tracing filter (e.g. `info`, `debug`, `adk_codeact_monty=debug`).
# RUST_LOG=warn
